&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.eig.org.uk/guides/Guide%20to%20the%20Pyrotechnic%20Articles%20(Safety)%20Regulations.pdf"&gt;Download guidance on pyrotechnics regulations from the EIG website (PDF, 3.15MB)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

