&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tables containing data supplied by local authorities and industry bodies and those relating to bus service provision are outside the scope of National Statistics.  The Department’s view is that all statistics which are not designated as National Statistics are robust and have been produced to a suitable standard.&lt;/p&gt;

